---
layout: default
body_id: home
---
- site.latest_posts.each do |post|
  .entry
    %h2== <a href="#{post.url}" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to #{post.title}">#{post.title}</a>
    .information== Posted on #{post.date.strftime("%d %b %Y")}
    .content= post.content

- site.older_posts.each do |post|
  .older_entry
    %h3== <a href="#{post.url}">#{post.title}</a>
    .information== #{post.date.strftime("%d %b %Y")}